# JDBC is a SE API that allows developer to establish connction to a Database

# this api gives complete control on the SQL statements

#Steps to Connect

1. Coonection object
2. Statement Object
3. Execute the Sql statement on the Statement object

# Statement class

execute -- can be used for all sql statement tyeps (DDL, DML, DQL) -- Returns boolean
executeUpdate -- can be used on DML statements primarily and also on DDL -- returns a number (int)
executeQuery -- can be used only for select statements -- returns resultset
exeuteBatch -- can be used only for DML statements -- returns a int[]

# ResultSet

getInt
getString
getDate
getDouble

